{"tid":849074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸仔Brooklyn意大利偷拍大媽 被轟歧視：不要再來中國","createTime":"2018-10-05T11:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T08:23:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"65811a76cbee2d97469dfdd68288ac53fd9d3bc5","tid":849074,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"碧咸大仔Brooklyn近日到意大利遊玩，一向醉心攝影嘅佢，偷拍咗兩張亞洲人士照片，並於Instagram留言：「這裡不像意大利了」，其中一張照片看到大媽乘船出海，另一張則係一名女子遊超市，即被中國網民解讀為諷刺遊意大利嘅中國人，砲轟佢種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n目前正是中國十一黃金周假期，似乎Brooklyn唔習慣觀光景點湧現大批中國遊客，其留言公開後即被中國網民留言聲討，紛紛到其IG留言鬧爆，要佢為自己言行道歉，連碧咸及Victoria都遭殃，有網民甚至於兩人Ig留言叫佢哋好好管教兒子，唔好再嚟中國，話「中國唔歡迎你哋」，而現時Brooklyn已將相關照片刪走，並IG改為非公開避風頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181005/58760413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58760413&d=dzHijIxb1BJdM2dR2xKuSQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a2155b98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58760413&h=a111cee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181005/58760413</a>"},{"pid":"c871eb5b64985bece9d29028a588fbbd615cbadf","tid":849074,"uid":89402,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"佢都唔晞罕黎中國啦<br />\n人地都去埋啲高級啲既城市<br />\n心諗咁都仲見到啲中國人 <br />\n比著我都屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40509c31a41f67296864b3456a9c59b13fd8f461","tid":849074,"uid":70786,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"支那人又玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b9ff2334a1ada99e0a9fffa45935dac8e35df4","tid":849074,"uid":27416,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"佢可以唔理啫<br />\n佢老豆仲要去個邊掘金<img src=\"/assets/faces